      background:${color};
      border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.6);
      box-shadow:0 0 0 4px ${color}44,0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.5);
    "></div>`,
    iconSize: [16, 16],
    iconAnchor: [8, 8]
  });
}

